      <title>美联储巴尔金希望通胀趋势持续扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/fed-s-barkin-wants-sustained-broadening-inflation-trend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士满联邦储备银行行长托马斯·巴尔金表示，美联储应该看到“几个月”的通胀数据，他希望看到随着美联储决定降息时机，这一趋势得以维持并扩大（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/fed-s-barkin-wants-sustained-broadening-inflation-trend</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利扭转转瞬即逝的看涨预期，赫兹股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/hertz-falls-as-morgan-stanley-reverses-fleeting-bullish-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利在一月中旬开始看好赫兹全球控股公司，理由是这家租赁汽车巨头正在对其电动汽车车队做出积极的改变。该银行现在已经改变了方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/hertz-falls-as-morgan-stanley-reverses-fleeting-bullish-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国初请失业金人数三周来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/us-jobless-claims-fall-for-first-time-in-three-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据劳工部数据，截至 2 月 3 日当周，美国首次申请失业救济人数减少 9,000 人，至 218,000 人。彭博社经济学家调查的预测中位数为 220,000。迈克·麦基报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/us-jobless-claims-fall-for-first-time-in-three-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尔金表示美联储有时间对降息保持耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/barkin-says-fed-has-time-to-be-patient-on-cutting-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士满联邦储备银行行长托马斯·巴尔金(Thomas Barkin)重申，政策制定者有时间对降息时机保持耐心，并指出强劲的劳动力市场和持续的通货紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/barkin-says-fed-has-time-to-be-patient-on-cutting-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪士尼首席财务官谈削减成本，纳尔逊·佩尔茨，体育捆绑包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/disney-cfo-on-cutting-costs-nelson-peltz-sports-bundle-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华特迪士尼公司首席财务官休·约翰斯顿 (Hugh Johnston) 谈论了削减成本、与福克斯公司 (Fox Corp.) 和华纳兄弟探索频道 (Warner Bros. Discovery) 合作组建新的流媒体服务以及抵御激进投资者纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 挑战的努力。他在“彭博监视”节目中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-08/disney-cfo-on-cutting-costs-nelson-peltz-sports-bundle-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:59:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯与高盛、花旗联手出售沙特阿美股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/saudi-arabia-said-to-line-up-goldman-citi-for-aramco-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，沙特阿拉伯将聘请花旗集团、高盛集团和汇丰控股等银行对沙特阿美进行二次股票出售，这笔交易将筹集约 200 亿美元，是近年来规模最大的发行之一。此事说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/saudi-arabia-said-to-line-up-goldman-citi-for-aramco-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:52:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apollo 利润飙升 31%，利率提振信贷、保险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/apollo-profit-soars-31-as-interest-rates-buoy-credit-insurance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司(Apollo Global Management Inc.)公布的利润超出了华尔街的预期，因为利率上升提振了这家另类资产管理公司不断增长的信贷和保险业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/apollo-profit-soars-31-as-interest-rates-buoy-credit-insurance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
